Class AssessmentProfile

java.lang.Object
  es.eucm.eadandroid.common.data.assessment.AssessmentProfile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Cloneable
public class AssessmentProfile
extends Object
implements Cloneable

Stores an assessment profile. Each profile contains the path of the xml file where it is stored (relative to the zip file), along with the list of assessment rules defined in the profile
